Come hang out!

Meet the new @SamsungMobileUSA #GalaxyTabS7FE 5G, which launched today in the US. A true Fan Edition for those looking for a more affordable and essential alternative to the Galaxy Tab S7+. Stay tuned as we have a lot of content planned, including a full interview with Samsung’s Hassan Anjum, Director and Head of Product Marketing and New Computing, which airs tomorrow. It’s been a year since we last caught up, so look out for what’s new! For now, here are some of the specs:
 
- 12.4”, 2560x1600 (WQXGA), TFT LCD
- S Pen included in the box
- Optional Keyboard case
- Android 11.0 
- Qualcomm SDM 750G
- 4G RAM / 64GB Expandable Storage
- 8MP Rear Camera / 5MP Front Camera 
- 10,090 mAh Battery
- Wi-Fi / 5G Variant
 
Starting tomorrow, the 5G variant, priced at $669, will be available for purchase, with the Wi-Fi variant at $529.99 available for pre-order. What do you think of this new Fan Edition tablet?
